Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.30,0:01:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紫吴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.04,0:01:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.74,0:01:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是关于5月1日的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.24,0:01:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我那天下午可以出去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.54,0:01:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以呀 那天正好没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.28,0:01:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么？要和小花他们出去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.32,0:01:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对 那天是母亲的忌日 想去扫墓一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.56,0:01:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 都一周年忌了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.96,0:01:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 但也没有特别准备什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.67,0:01:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉 没办法一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.74,0:01:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别这么说啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.97,0:01:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.94,0:02:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以一起去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.21,0:02:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.74,0:02:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想扫扫你母亲的墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.65,0:02:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢 我妈妈一定会很高兴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.52,0:02:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.75,0:02:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那天如果没事的话 你也一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.59,0:02:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那王子也要去罗 阿夹呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.26,0:02:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道 他什么都没说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.87,0:02:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日子应该会喜欢阿夹他们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.60,0:02:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定可以跟他们打成一片的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.60,0:02:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,橘子 橘子 我要吃了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.60,0:02:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.14,0:02:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后终于将快要无法忍受的阿夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.88,0:02:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从背后一副饿虎扑羊的态势紧紧的抱住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.08,0:02:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那可不行啊 代志大条哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.52,0:02:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你母亲过世…已经一年了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.06,0:02:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但现在仍觉得哪天她会突然跑出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.43,0:03:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,边笑着边说"不好意思 不好意思"呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.84,0:03:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不妙 气氛搞的有点冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.24,0:03:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过这也表示今日子很了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.18,0:03:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像"环七红蝴蝶"传说般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.15,0:03:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那雄伟的"装饰卡车"让人一辈子都忘不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.45,0:03:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,装饰卡车指的就是额头凸出的卡车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.69,0:03:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乱讲！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.93,0:03:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都能去扫墓就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.30,0:03:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.48,0:03:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 我也要去扫墓喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.85,0:03:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干嘛跟我说呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.72,0:03:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啰唆 我说要去就要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.83,0:04:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在画什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.80,0:04:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好小的一间庙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.17,0:04:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.97,0:04:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我比较喜欢随意的气氛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.57,0:04:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对庙这么讲究干什么嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.54,0:04:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很奇怪吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.48,0:04:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也没啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.78,0:04:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.51,0:04:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还好天气变好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.92,0:04:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近老是阴晴不定 我还有点担心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.22,0:04:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能妈妈也很高兴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.22,0:04:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为你们大家都来了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.34,0:04:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.57,0:04:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天是扫墓的好日子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.64,0:04:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.21,0:04:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么装扮嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.95,0:04:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说"什么"是啥意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.82,0:04:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然太朴素了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.72,0:04:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太阴了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.95,0:05:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鱼谷…莫非这是特攻队的衣服？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.93,0:05:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦 你很内行嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.06,0:05:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这可是今日子给我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.16,0:05:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正统红蝶特攻队队长穿的衣服唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.13,0:05:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红蝶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.40,0:05:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我妈当年的艺名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.97,0:05:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艺名？还笑得那么开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.94,0:05:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啦！该到的都到了 我们快出发吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.38,0:05:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很兴奋 超兴奋的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.45,0:05:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？很干净耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.85,0:05:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人来过了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.86,0:05:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.63,0:05:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为爷爷清楚妈妈喜欢吃的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.33,0:05:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爷爷？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.56,0:05:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 那位老伯呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.90,0:05:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.83,0:05:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那位爷爷是哪一边的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.07,0:05:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是爸爸的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.54,0:05:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟今日子那边的父母就比较疏远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.78,0:06:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你父亲又为什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.61,0:06:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说因为感冒就这么走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.32,0:06:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当时我还小不太记得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.26,0:06:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈 我们来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.70,0:06:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.66,0:06:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爷爷都整理过了 好像没什么可做的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.67,0:06:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.14,0:06:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父亲走了 母亲也去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.61,0:06:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.01,0:06:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透为何能那么开朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.12,0:06:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总是笑颜洋溢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.39,0:06:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意外当天的事我还记得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.39,0:06:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上课中她突然被老师叫去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.63,0:06:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谈了一阵后…就飞奔而去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.53,0:06:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,两位朋友也紧追在后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.93,0:06:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,教室顿然一阵骚动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.27,0:07:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当时我还在想是不是她的家人遭到什么意外了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.28,0:07:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对于那件事情 我只是淡淡的猜想了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.42,0:07:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我对当时的本田透这个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.35,0:07:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也只有这样淡淡的印象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.76,0:07:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但现在却同住一个屋檐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.20,0:07:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如此的亲近…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.83,0:07:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希 你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.13,0:07:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很漂亮的花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.48,0:07:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己能够这样子跟她一同欢笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.05,0:07:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不可思议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.29,0:07:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准备好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.40,0:07:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来很好吃呢 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.77,0:07:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别在墓地野餐呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.53,0:08:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.37,0:08:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,热闹一点今日子也会很开心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.37,0:08:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被庙里的人发现了怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.34,0:08:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,道歉就好了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.48,0:08:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是一般是不会这样做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.71,0:08:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之别唠唠叨叨的 快坐下来吧 阿夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.51,0:08:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样站着让人很不自在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.55,0:08:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹 要吃点什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.62,0:08:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,随便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.49,0:08:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.85,0:08:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鱼谷你们跟小透的妈妈很熟吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.86,0:08:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她很照顾我哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.63,0:08:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,认识以前就是传说中的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.06,0:08:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很崇拜她呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.50,0:08:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传说人物？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.20,0:08:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是红蝶传说呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.63,0:08:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什么传说嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.07,0:08:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.07,0:08:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日子一骑上摩托车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.61,0:08:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就好像蝴蝶起舞般 后面的尾灯闪烁个不停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.11,0:08:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全听不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.41,0:08:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么会听不懂呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.22,0:08:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个也很好吃\N你也真没想像力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.15,0:08:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇 这个也很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.02,0:08:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了 你别讲话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.59,0:08:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这个浑蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.89,0:08:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的太好吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.13,0:09:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透很努力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.87,0:09:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,经过一年后的现在可以这样开怀的笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.91,0:09:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那段期间一定斥责过无数次软弱的自己吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.75,0:09:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果换成我失去了重要的亲人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.05,0:09:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就没把握一年后是否可以这样的笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.96,0:09:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比如要是小透死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.87,0:09:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞不好会因为太痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.30,0:09:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而甚至想要忘掉曾与她交往的所有一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.27,0:09:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但小透她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.55,0:09:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,却那么努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.89,0:10:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想…不管怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.02,0:10:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实也多亏他们两人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.26,0:10:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们三个之间的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.33,0:10:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近愈来愈好不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.50,0:10:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.14,0:10:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知哪天谁会先说出喜欢小透的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.31,0:10:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.84,0:10:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不会那么轻易的承认他们的交往呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.61,0:10:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是小透的婆婆吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.18,0:10:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也是半开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.28,0:10:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那有一半是真的罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.02,0:10:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩由希还有草摩夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.66,0:10:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎依旧无法跳脱出心中的那块阴影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.60,0:10:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种事每个人多少都有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.57,0:10:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是他们两人算是严重的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.47,0:10:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要那个怨恨还在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.51,0:10:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们大概没有谈恋爱的心情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.14,0:10:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且我还想强调一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.71,0:11:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们俩对这种事又特别迟钝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.65,0:11:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这点小透也一样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.05,0:11:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但有时也会在莫名其妙中突然开花结果的情况呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.76,0:11:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要 我才不要小透嫁出去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.30,0:11:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光想就想哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.83,0:11:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想太多了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.37,0:11:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦一天之后的茶是最香的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.37,0:11:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天的扫墓真愉快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.94,0:11:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真高兴终于能把由希与阿夹介绍给妈妈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.95,0:11:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.65,0:11:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们两人很照顾我喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.76,0:11:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪天要是能再介绍紫吴给你认识就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.73,0:11:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈 我住在这里 每天都和大家过得很愉快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.61,0:12:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以请你放心 继续保佑我喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.21,0:12:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.90,0:12:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天真是谢谢你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.23,0:12:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪有 反倒吃了你一顿呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.04,0:12:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透 你的下厨功夫愈来愈好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.44,0:12:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来你随时可以嫁人去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.15,0:12:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抛下我一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.55,0:12:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.92,0:12:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.05,0:12:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快躲起来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.35,0:12:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红叶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.29,0:12:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在我们正在玩警察捉小偷的游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.36,0:12:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是小偷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.92,0:12:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红叶 你再躲也没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.03,0:12:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了 被发现了 我得走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.43,0:12:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看前面呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.20,0:12:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发现红叶了 快呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.01,0:12:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是精力旺盛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.51,0:12:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.84,0:12:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看前面呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.34,0:13:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但怎么看都像男生在追女生似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.88,0:13:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他应该比较像妈妈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.68,0:13:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.29,0:13:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 人家不是常说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.15,0:13:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男生像妈妈 女生像爸爸吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.99,0:13:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比起妈妈 小透也比较像爸爸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.29,0:13:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该说是像爷爷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.70,0:13:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 红叶的父母好像也没来参加开学典礼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.64,0:13:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一位白发的男生也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.67,0:13:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么说来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.04,0:13:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩家的人好像都绝口不提他们的父母呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.86,0:13:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像很重呢 我也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.49,0:13:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红叶 怎么会在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.96,0:13:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这栋大厦是爸爸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.66,0:13:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是说你爸爸在这里工作吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.17,0:13:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对 但是…不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.67,0:14:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟你说 爸爸他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.21,0:14:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.21,0:14:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来你在这里呀 刚刚老板一直再找你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.75,0:14:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你转告爸爸 我要回去了请他不要担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.02,0:14:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.59,0:14:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少爷？老板？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.53,0:14:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是爸爸的第12栋大楼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.50,0:14:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来是这个意思呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.03,0:14:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有照片喔 你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.94,0:14:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你父亲好帅喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.27,0:14:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.78,0:14:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好温柔好漂亮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.21,0:14:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很美呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.62,0:14:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸呢…爸爸是草摩的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.69,0:14:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸是在大学时认识妈妈才结婚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.82,0:14:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸好厉害居然能娶到妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.86,0:15:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有啊 我还有个妹妹呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.37,0:15:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她叫小桃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.67,0:15:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小桃和妈妈长得很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.84,0:15:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也有其他兄弟姊妹呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.57,0:15:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 她今年小学2年级
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.51,0:15:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但小桃不是十二生肖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.11,0:15:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我告诉你她和妈妈好像喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.48,0:15:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还很会撒娇呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.18,0:15:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像跟屁虫般 老是黏在妈妈身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.32,0:15:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但她不太会讲话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.19,0:15:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舌头不太灵光但真的很可爱喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.69,0:15:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讲得兴高采烈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.83,0:15:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈和小桃都会来接爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.13,0:15:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 大概快来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.14,0:15:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不就可以一起回家了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.40,0:15:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀 能那样就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.57,0:15:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但妈妈不知道我的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.61,0:15:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.85,0:15:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红叶 这时间你在这里干嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.65,0:15:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说曹操 曹操就到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.82,0:16:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那这位就是小桃罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.13,0:16:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但红叶还是比较像妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.60,0:16:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的朋友在这里打工啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.70,0:16:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我来找她玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.67,0:16:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈不知道我的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.24,0:16:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样呀 但这里不是玩耍的地方喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.55,0:16:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.45,0:16:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.65,0:16:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太晚回去的话你妈妈也会担心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.46,0:16:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系 我现在就要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.69,0:16:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗 那要直接回去喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.63,0:16:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.63,0:16:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小桃 我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.60,0:16:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸可能等不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.28,0:17:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真倒楣 被发现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.05,0:17:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下得向爸爸自首才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.29,0:17:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红叶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.17,0:17:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈不知道我的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.47,0:17:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她因为记忆移除 已经忘了我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.81,0:17:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈一直以为我是草摩家某人的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.88,0:17:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被怪物附身的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.95,0:17:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比10月10日预产期早两个月出生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.29,0:17:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遇见喜欢的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.72,0:17:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和喜欢的人结婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.56,0:17:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并生下对方的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.43,0:17:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但如果拥抱那个孩子的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.93,0:17:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就会变成奇怪的动物宝宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.40,0:17:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.57,0:17:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这对妈妈而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.97,0:17:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是多么的绝望啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.61,0:18:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生下被怪物附身的小孩的母亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.48,0:18:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是变得太过于保护
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.05,0:18:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然就是受到万分惊吓的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.85,0:18:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我妈妈就是受到万分惊吓的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.16,0:18:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全身受到惊吓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.13,0:18:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽量不看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.49,0:18:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但尽管如此 她还是很焦虑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.96,0:18:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总是歇斯底里的大叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.20,0:18:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在回想起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.00,0:18:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈是崩溃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.97,0:18:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像佳菜那样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.07,0:18:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红叶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.64,0:18:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈也许无可救药了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.38,0:18:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但如果忘了你的事或许可以治好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.25,0:18:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.19,0:18:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但爸爸会连妈妈的份加倍爱你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.39,0:18:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红叶如果也爱妈妈就救救妈妈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.93,0:18:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的要忘掉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.17,0:18:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会后悔吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.31,0:19:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我这辈子最后悔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.58,0:19:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是生下那怪胎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.95,0:19:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,后来我就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.46,0:19:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从妈妈的记忆中消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.03,0:19:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈恢复得很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.16,0:19:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,两个月后就会笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.27,0:19:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我这样做 不知道对妈妈有没有帮助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.84,0:19:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来他一直暗地里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.35,0:19:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从远方小心翼翼地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.05,0:19:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不被发现地守护着妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.75,0:19:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也是这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.69,0:19:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我是这么想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.59,0:19:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想珍惜这份回忆勇敢的活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.59,0:19:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使那是一个令人哀伤的记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.43,0:20:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个让我痛苦的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.27,0:20:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚至是一个让我想忘掉的过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.64,0:20:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要面对它 不逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.91,0:20:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信有一天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.85,0:20:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一天我会成为能够胜过这份回忆的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.42,0:20:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是这么深信的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.59,0:20:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我想这么相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.16,0:20:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我希望没有任何一个回忆是可以遗忘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.73,0:20:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.47,0:20:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实我也不希望妈妈忘了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.37,0:20:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我不可以太任性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.28,0:20:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是秘密喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.16,0:21:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也…我也相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.87,0:21:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是何种回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.78,0:21:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都要深藏心里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.01,0:21:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并且深信着它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.98,0:21:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我希望没有任何一个回忆是可以遗忘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.96,0:21:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一天一定会成为能够胜过这些的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.63,0:21:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且总有一天能够超越这一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.91,0:21:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成为美好的记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.54,0:21:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信着

